{"title":"告别","authors":["杜华林"],"dates":[{"year":1954,"month":1,"day":17}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"告别"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杜华林"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喝干你这杯酒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我把穿旧的蓝军装，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一齐带走。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跟我握手。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"别惊动了大海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叫她难受。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同志，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你要记住："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱们伙用的那门大炮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不能叫它生锈。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是祖国的召唤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我去参加建设，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你在这里驻守。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"别了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我马上就走。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不要当我是离开部队，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只当我去参加一次战斗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从战斗走向战斗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要像学开大炮那样，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学会扳机器的电钮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"放心吧！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我懂得："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"既是个光荣的战士，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就要做生产的能手。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}